WEBVTT

00:00:02.043 --> 00:00:04.754
WRITTEN BY HYUGA NATSU

00:01:33.259 --> 00:01:34.928
I can’t believe it!

00:01:35.637 --> 00:01:38.640
{\an8}Serving anyone other than Lady Gyokuyou?!

00:01:39.265 --> 00:01:40.850
<i>Even if you say that...</i>

00:01:41.643 --> 00:01:42.477
There’s...

00:01:43.061 --> 00:01:46.397
There’s a ghost...

00:01:46.481 --> 00:01:47.732
in the palace bathhouse!

00:01:51.111 --> 00:01:54.739
Why not consult
Lord Jinshi about it first?

00:01:55.615 --> 00:01:57.200
<i>After hearing something like that,</i>

00:01:57.283 --> 00:01:59.911
<i>there’s no way I can just ignore it.</i>

00:02:02.163 --> 00:02:04.791
- Maomao.
<i>- As expected.</i>

00:02:04.874 --> 00:02:07.669
<i>The task has fallen to me.</i>

00:02:08.253 --> 00:02:09.420
{\an8}You called for me?

00:02:16.928 --> 00:02:18.638
<i>Damn.</i>

00:02:18.721 --> 00:02:20.932
<i>I got an ox bezoar and completely forgot,</i>

00:02:21.015 --> 00:02:24.352
<i>but during that last hunt,
I learned an outrageous secret.</i>

00:02:24.435 --> 00:02:26.396
<i>All men in the rear palace,</i>

00:02:26.479 --> 00:02:29.357
<i>aside from the Emperor, are eunuchs.</i>

00:02:29.440 --> 00:02:31.359
<i>However, Lord Jinshi is not.</i>

00:02:31.442 --> 00:02:34.112
<i>He possesses a rather impressive frog.</i>

00:02:37.949 --> 00:02:40.160
So, what is your request today?

00:02:40.827 --> 00:02:43.621
It seems that a ghost has been appearing
in a certain consort’s chambers.

00:02:43.705 --> 00:02:47.584
Oh my, how dreadful.

00:02:49.168 --> 00:02:51.129
Which consort is it?

00:02:51.212 --> 00:02:52.964
I must go visit her.

00:02:53.047 --> 00:02:54.382
Lady Gyokuyou,

00:02:54.465 --> 00:02:57.260
you mustn’t go outside in your condition.

00:02:57.343 --> 00:02:59.262
In that case, I shall send someone.

00:02:59.846 --> 00:03:01.472
You're right.

00:03:01.556 --> 00:03:04.517
Hongniang, how about

00:03:04.601 --> 00:03:06.352
you and Maomao go together?

00:03:06.436 --> 00:03:10.189
Lady Gyokuyou,
this is a confidential matter,

00:03:10.273 --> 00:03:12.191
so please refrain from visiting.

00:03:12.901 --> 00:03:14.527
With that in mind,

00:03:14.611 --> 00:03:17.196
may I have her back?

00:03:18.072 --> 00:03:20.700
{\an8}If you'd like to "borrow" her,
I’ll give her to you.

00:03:25.121 --> 00:03:26.873
<i>This exchange again?</i>

00:03:27.749 --> 00:03:30.293
No, I want you to "return" her.

00:03:31.085 --> 00:03:33.755
Return Maomao to me.

00:03:35.465 --> 00:03:36.883
Once I'm done and give her to you,

00:03:36.966 --> 00:03:39.719
no matter what you ask her,

00:03:40.470 --> 00:03:41.471
{\an8}she won’t say a word.

00:03:42.388 --> 00:03:44.599
I’ll make sure of that.

00:03:46.643 --> 00:03:49.270
Well, let’s be on our way.

00:03:59.072 --> 00:04:02.367
You two...
Did something happen during the hunt?

00:04:03.660 --> 00:04:05.578
It's because of a frog.

00:04:06.871 --> 00:04:07.747
A frog?

00:04:08.665 --> 00:04:11.626
<i>Considering the secret
I have to take to my grave,</i>

00:04:11.709 --> 00:04:14.254
<i>maybe the ox bezoar wasn't worth it.</i>

00:04:15.713 --> 00:04:17.006
We've been expecting you.

00:04:25.473 --> 00:04:28.935
<i>Just how much does Lord Gaoshun know?</i>

00:04:29.435 --> 00:04:33.398
<i>Or perhaps, he is also not a eunuch?</i>

00:04:34.732 --> 00:04:37.402
<i>Never mind.
Thinking about it won’t change anything.</i>

00:04:41.281 --> 00:04:43.408
Good day, Lady Lishu.

00:04:44.534 --> 00:04:45.368
Lord Jinshi!

00:04:45.451 --> 00:04:46.744
Could you guide us to

00:04:46.828 --> 00:04:50.123
the bathhouse where the ghost was seen?

00:04:51.749 --> 00:04:52.583
Yes.

00:04:53.751 --> 00:04:55.503
<i>Aren't they being a little too obvious?</i>

00:04:55.586 --> 00:04:59.215
<i>For a high-ranking consort,
this is quite concerning.</i>

00:04:59.882 --> 00:05:01.050
This way.

00:05:03.720 --> 00:05:07.015
The changing room is in the front,
and the bath is in the back.

00:05:08.558 --> 00:05:11.644
But Lady Lishu saw the strange shadow

00:05:11.728 --> 00:05:13.980
from this storage room window.

00:05:15.315 --> 00:05:17.066
What kind of shadow did you see?

00:05:17.650 --> 00:05:19.152
W-Well...

00:05:20.361 --> 00:05:23.072
Are you still going on about that?

00:05:23.156 --> 00:05:25.700
It must have been a trick of the light.

00:05:25.783 --> 00:05:29.954
Lady Lishu just wants attention.

00:05:32.415 --> 00:05:36.836
Making such a fuss over something trivial.

00:05:36.919 --> 00:05:38.296
It is

00:05:39.005 --> 00:05:42.717
a head lady-in-waiting’s duty
to correct such behavior.

00:05:43.301 --> 00:05:45.178
Or do former food tasters

00:05:45.261 --> 00:05:47.972
not even understand that?

00:05:48.056 --> 00:05:49.474
My apologies.

00:05:49.557 --> 00:05:51.476
<i>Judging by her tone,</i>

00:05:51.559 --> 00:05:54.562
<i>that arrogant attendant
must be the former head lady-in-waiting.</i>

00:05:54.645 --> 00:05:57.231
<i>Losing her position to the food taster</i>

00:05:57.315 --> 00:06:00.693
<i>must have left her bitter enough
to spew sarcasm daily.</i>

00:06:03.571 --> 00:06:05.323
<i>That hairpin...?</i>

00:06:06.240 --> 00:06:08.326
Don’t you agree?

00:06:09.077 --> 00:06:10.661
Perhaps.

00:06:11.496 --> 00:06:15.541
However, listening to the consorts
is also my duty.

00:06:15.625 --> 00:06:18.002
Could you refrain from taking over my job?

00:06:19.545 --> 00:06:20.421
Understood.

00:06:23.341 --> 00:06:25.134
I feel a bit thirsty.

00:06:26.427 --> 00:06:28.096
I’ll bring tea at once!

00:06:28.179 --> 00:06:30.473
- I will!
- No, let me!

00:06:30.556 --> 00:06:32.225
Let me!

00:06:32.308 --> 00:06:34.519
Now then, Lady Lishu,

00:06:34.602 --> 00:06:36.312
please tell me in detail.

00:06:38.564 --> 00:06:39.816
Y... Yes.

00:06:41.567 --> 00:06:44.570
<i>He sent everyone away to make sure
Lady Lishu doesn’t shrink back.</i>

00:06:45.363 --> 00:06:49.826
It happened after my usual bath.

00:06:50.743 --> 00:06:52.995
<i>I actually prefer lukewarm water,</i>

00:06:53.079 --> 00:06:55.832
<i>but the maids always prepare hot baths,</i>

00:06:56.666 --> 00:07:00.211
<i>so I make it a habit to bathe
a little later when the water cools.</i>

00:07:01.212 --> 00:07:03.089
<i>I kind of knew,</i>

00:07:04.090 --> 00:07:05.925
<i>but the maids</i>

00:07:06.008 --> 00:07:08.553
<i>don’t seem too fond of me.</i>

00:07:09.345 --> 00:07:12.807
<i>Since my time in the nunnery,
I’ve always bathed alone.</i>

00:07:13.349 --> 00:07:16.227
<i>Only Kanan, I mean...</i>

00:07:16.310 --> 00:07:19.063
<i>the head lady-in-waiting,
helped me with my clothes.</i>

00:07:19.564 --> 00:07:21.357
<i>When I was wiping myself dry,</i>

00:07:21.441 --> 00:07:24.277
<i>I felt hot, so I lifted the blinds.</i>

00:07:24.360 --> 00:07:28.281
<i>Even though the window was shut,</i>

00:07:28.364 --> 00:07:30.241
<i>the curtain swayed.</i>

00:07:31.576 --> 00:07:34.036
<i>And there, grinning, was a white face...</i>

00:07:34.120 --> 00:07:35.872
<i>dancing.</i>

00:07:37.081 --> 00:07:40.042
While staring... right at me.

00:07:44.630 --> 00:07:47.758
Could there have been someone nearby?

00:07:49.135 --> 00:07:51.888
No. Kanan was the only one close by.

00:07:51.971 --> 00:07:54.557
She saw the same ghost too!

00:07:55.850 --> 00:07:58.603
{\an8}When I tried to get closer to identify it...

00:07:59.395 --> 00:08:01.397
<i>The ghost vanished,</i>

00:08:02.190 --> 00:08:06.444
<i>and the curtain suddenly stopped moving.</i>

00:08:07.612 --> 00:08:11.616
<i>The windows leading outside were all shut,</i>

00:08:11.699 --> 00:08:13.784
<i>so there was no wind.</i>

00:08:13.868 --> 00:08:16.704
<i>And yet, the curtain swayed.</i>

00:08:18.122 --> 00:08:21.209
<i>No wonder they were frightened
and believed it was a ghost.</i>

00:08:21.959 --> 00:08:24.253
<i>But this layout is odd.</i>

00:08:24.337 --> 00:08:26.422
<i>In the Crystal and Jade Pavilion,</i>

00:08:26.506 --> 00:08:28.508
<i>the bathhouses are separate structures</i>

00:08:28.591 --> 00:08:30.718
<i>with lounging areas.</i>

00:08:31.594 --> 00:08:35.264
<i>Who builds a storage room
next to a bathhouse?</i>

00:08:38.476 --> 00:08:41.437
Was that room originally a storage room?

00:08:42.271 --> 00:08:44.357
{\an8}No, it wasn't...

00:08:44.982 --> 00:08:48.319
{\an8}- Then why did they turn it into storage?
- That's because...

00:08:52.323 --> 00:08:55.868
If you look here, you’ll understand.

00:09:01.999 --> 00:09:03.209
I see.

00:09:03.876 --> 00:09:05.962
It’s covered in mold.

00:09:06.587 --> 00:09:08.297
<i>The maids of the Jade Pavilion</i>

00:09:08.381 --> 00:09:09.924
<i>would have investigated</i>

00:09:10.007 --> 00:09:12.468
<i>and prevented mold from forming,</i>

00:09:13.052 --> 00:09:16.138
<i>but expecting that the maids here
would do the same is unrealistic.</i>

00:09:16.681 --> 00:09:19.517
<i>In the end, they turned it into
a storage room to cover it up.</i>

00:09:25.231 --> 00:09:28.609
<i>It's possible that the foundation
itself might be rotting.</i>

00:09:29.443 --> 00:09:31.779
Is this building older than the others?

00:09:32.280 --> 00:09:34.824
No, it’s actually newer.

00:09:34.907 --> 00:09:37.660
It was built when Lady Lishu
entered the palace.

00:09:38.160 --> 00:09:39.787
<i>It’s in this state after just a few years?</i>

00:09:40.663 --> 00:09:43.749
<i>Lady Lishu mentioned the curtain moving.</i>

00:09:46.711 --> 00:09:48.379
Show me the bath.

00:09:52.216 --> 00:09:53.050
<i>There it is.</i>

00:09:53.884 --> 00:09:55.219
<i>This hole should lead</i>

00:09:55.303 --> 00:09:58.055
<i>to the waterway of the rear palace.</i>

00:09:58.806 --> 00:10:00.057
- Lady Lishu.
- Oh?

00:10:00.641 --> 00:10:02.518
On the day the ghost appeared,

00:10:02.602 --> 00:10:05.479
did you, by any chance,
accidentally drain the bathwater?

00:10:07.148 --> 00:10:08.190
How did you know?

00:10:08.274 --> 00:10:09.692
I knew it!

00:10:10.443 --> 00:10:11.861
<i>Sealed windows,</i>

00:10:12.361 --> 00:10:13.904
<i>swaying curtains,</i>

00:10:13.988 --> 00:10:16.782
<i>and a drained bathtub.</i>

00:10:17.325 --> 00:10:19.577
<i>If my deduction is correct,</i>

00:10:19.660 --> 00:10:21.912
<i>the dancing ghost is...</i>

00:10:29.503 --> 00:10:30.671
Lord Gaoshun,

00:10:30.755 --> 00:10:33.716
could you help me move this shelf?

00:10:33.799 --> 00:10:34.925
Certainly.

00:10:39.388 --> 00:10:41.015
This is terrible.

00:10:41.098 --> 00:10:43.434
Yes, it's rotting badly.

00:10:45.353 --> 00:10:47.730
<i>The floor is warped and creating gaps.</i>

00:10:48.230 --> 00:10:50.024
<i>That would mean...</i>

00:10:50.107 --> 00:10:53.486
Could we check if there's
a water channel beneath here?

00:10:53.569 --> 00:10:56.489
I'll prepare the architectural plans
immediately.

00:10:58.491 --> 00:11:01.285
- Here they are.
- Thank you.

00:11:04.038 --> 00:11:06.791
As I suspected, there’s
a water channel beneath this floor.

00:11:07.458 --> 00:11:09.210
If hot water flows under here,

00:11:09.293 --> 00:11:12.296
the steam would cause the floor
and walls to rot more easily.

00:11:12.380 --> 00:11:13.547
<i>And the steam</i>

00:11:13.631 --> 00:11:17.093
<i>rising through these gaps
would create airflow,</i>

00:11:17.176 --> 00:11:18.803
<i>making the curtains sway.</i>

00:11:20.304 --> 00:11:23.682
Then... what was that face I saw?

00:11:26.394 --> 00:11:27.228
Ah, that.

00:11:31.440 --> 00:11:33.275
Um, that is...

00:11:34.360 --> 00:11:35.861
That mirror is

00:11:35.945 --> 00:11:39.031
important to me.
Please handle it with care.

00:11:39.740 --> 00:11:42.660
Understood. How long has this been here?

00:11:42.743 --> 00:11:45.162
I used to use it often.

00:11:45.246 --> 00:11:48.249
But now I have the mirror
that was sent by the envoy.

00:11:49.083 --> 00:11:51.252
<i>The envoy’s mirror is made of glass</i>

00:11:51.335 --> 00:11:53.587
<i>and reflects far better
than a bronze mirror.</i>

00:11:53.671 --> 00:11:57.174
<i>It’s understandable that
she put her old mirror away. Even so...</i>

00:11:57.675 --> 00:11:59.844
Do you polish this every day?

00:12:00.970 --> 00:12:03.722
Yes, it was my mother’s.

00:12:05.224 --> 00:12:09.186
<i>At a glance,
it looks like an ordinary bronze mirror...</i>

00:12:11.063 --> 00:12:12.189
Lady Lishu,

00:12:12.273 --> 00:12:15.401
since we have the mirror here,
how about using it again?

00:12:16.735 --> 00:12:17.736
Please, go ahead.

00:12:21.157 --> 00:12:22.908
Use it...?

00:12:24.118 --> 00:12:27.746
It’s easier to see
if you use it in a bright spot.

00:12:33.169 --> 00:12:36.255
If you angle it this way,
you might get a clearer reflection.

00:12:45.139 --> 00:12:47.975
<i>I see, so that’s how it appears.</i>

00:12:48.058 --> 00:12:49.518
What does this mean?

00:12:50.102 --> 00:12:51.812
It’s called a "magic mirror."

00:12:51.896 --> 00:12:54.231
This is my first time seeing a real one.

00:12:54.315 --> 00:12:55.232
A magic mirror?

00:12:55.316 --> 00:12:58.027
<i>It’s also known as
a "transmission mirror."</i>

00:12:58.110 --> 00:13:00.613
<i>When light bounces off it,</i>

00:13:00.696 --> 00:13:02.740
<i>it mysteriously forms images or text.</i>

00:13:02.823 --> 00:13:05.993
<i>The technique involves engraving patterns
into the mirror’s surface</i>

00:13:06.076 --> 00:13:08.162
<i>during its creation.</i>

00:13:08.245 --> 00:13:10.581
It requires considerable craftsmanship,

00:13:10.664 --> 00:13:12.791
something my foster father once told me.

00:13:16.921 --> 00:13:20.090
<i>A polished mirror catches the moonlight,</i>

00:13:20.174 --> 00:13:21.175
<i>reflecting a face.</i>

00:13:22.051 --> 00:13:23.677
<i>Steam rises through the gaps,</i>

00:13:24.261 --> 00:13:25.638
<i>making the curtain sway.</i>

00:13:27.306 --> 00:13:31.101
<i>In conclusion, a series of coincidences</i>

00:13:31.185 --> 00:13:33.187
<i>created this "ghost."</i>

00:13:34.063 --> 00:13:38.400
That face... It looks like my late mother.

00:13:39.360 --> 00:13:40.945
Maybe she was angry

00:13:41.028 --> 00:13:44.823
because I stopped using her mirror.

00:13:45.366 --> 00:13:47.201
Maybe that’s why she appeared.

00:13:48.202 --> 00:13:49.954
{\an8}It was just a coincidence.

00:13:50.663 --> 00:13:52.998
I heard that she loved to dance.

00:13:53.082 --> 00:13:56.794
But after giving birth to me,
she fell ill and could no longer dance.

00:13:56.877 --> 00:13:59.171
And then she passed away.

00:13:59.255 --> 00:14:02.049
Maybe she became a ghost
so she could dance again.

00:14:02.841 --> 00:14:04.385
Ghosts don't--

00:14:13.936 --> 00:14:15.646
<i>At her age,</i>

00:14:15.729 --> 00:14:18.148
<i>she should be able to
enjoy life more freely.</i>

00:14:18.232 --> 00:14:21.026
<i>But polishing her mother’s mirror
every day</i>

00:14:21.110 --> 00:14:24.446
<i>might have been her way
of finding solace in the palace.</i>

00:14:25.614 --> 00:14:28.659
<i>I don’t understand
what it’s like to long for one’s mother.</i>

00:14:29.451 --> 00:14:32.204
<i>But to Lady Lishu,</i>

00:14:32.288 --> 00:14:34.999
<i>her mother must have been someone
worth cherishing.</i>

00:14:38.586 --> 00:14:40.754
I hope he likes it.

00:14:40.838 --> 00:14:42.256
Pardon the interruption.

00:14:42.339 --> 00:14:45.134
We've prepared tea outside.

00:14:49.388 --> 00:14:53.726
Lady Lishu, why are you crying?

00:14:53.809 --> 00:14:56.103
It’s improper to show such emotion
in front of everyone.

00:14:56.770 --> 00:15:00.482
<i>She speaks as if she’s a devoted maid,</i>

00:15:00.566 --> 00:15:03.277
<i>but her true nature seeps through.</i>

00:15:03.360 --> 00:15:05.154
<i>Such an obvious act.</i>

00:15:05.237 --> 00:15:07.656
Oh my, that mirror?

00:15:07.740 --> 00:15:10.534
You still have it?

00:15:11.785 --> 00:15:14.914
The envoy gifted you a far superior one,

00:15:14.997 --> 00:15:16.749
so you don’t need this anymore.

00:15:17.499 --> 00:15:20.002
- Why not bestow it upon someone else?
- Give it...

00:15:20.085 --> 00:15:21.712
Pardon?

00:15:22.421 --> 00:15:26.216
Give it back! Give it back!

00:15:28.886 --> 00:15:29.720
What is wrong with you!

00:15:30.596 --> 00:15:33.098
Such disgraceful behavior
in front of guests!

00:15:33.182 --> 00:15:36.352
That is something very precious
to Lady Lishu.

00:15:36.977 --> 00:15:40.606
Taking it without proper consideration
seems inappropriate.

00:15:51.075 --> 00:15:52.993
Was this item bestowed upon you?

00:15:55.079 --> 00:15:57.915
Even if it was,

00:15:57.998 --> 00:16:00.167
for a mere maid to wear an ornament

00:16:00.250 --> 00:16:02.336
bearing the crest
of a high-ranking consort...

00:16:04.213 --> 00:16:06.799
did you not find that inappropriate?

00:16:10.260 --> 00:16:13.764
<i>Lord Jinshi must have
known that Lady Lishu</i>

00:16:13.847 --> 00:16:15.683
<i>was being disregarded by her maids.</i>

00:16:16.558 --> 00:16:18.310
<i>He kept quiet</i>

00:16:18.394 --> 00:16:20.813
<i>to preserve her dignity.</i>

00:16:21.605 --> 00:16:25.401
<i>But with physical evidence,
he can finally put them in their place.</i>

00:16:26.777 --> 00:16:31.156
From now on, refrain from actions
that exceed your position.

00:16:43.877 --> 00:16:45.045
<i>He's terrifying.</i>

00:16:49.758 --> 00:16:52.177
- Isn't that him?
- So charming!

00:16:52.261 --> 00:16:55.055
Here to peek at the newcomers again?

00:16:56.640 --> 00:16:59.685
Yeah, yeah. I get it, Maomao.

00:17:01.103 --> 00:17:05.232
Young lady, are you researching more
anesthetic-like medicines again?

00:17:05.315 --> 00:17:06.233
Yes.

00:17:06.316 --> 00:17:10.112
They don’t make new eunuchs anymore,
so there’s no need to investigate that.

00:17:10.821 --> 00:17:14.575
By the way,
how do eunuchs enter the rear palace?

00:17:14.658 --> 00:17:16.618
Through surgery.

00:17:16.702 --> 00:17:17.828
No, I mean,

00:17:17.911 --> 00:17:20.831
how do they prove they’re eunuchs?

00:17:22.041 --> 00:17:24.752
In the past, a certificate was enough,

00:17:24.835 --> 00:17:26.795
but due to fraud,

00:17:27.838 --> 00:17:29.465
now they undergo a physical examination.

00:17:30.049 --> 00:17:30.924
They grab it?

00:17:31.008 --> 00:17:33.385
You’re too blunt, young lady!

00:17:34.178 --> 00:17:35.512
To prevent fraud,

00:17:35.596 --> 00:17:38.724
three officials from different departments
conduct the examination,

00:17:38.807 --> 00:17:40.642
and if nothing is there,
they’re allowed in.

00:17:40.726 --> 00:17:42.686
Are they only checked one time?

00:17:42.770 --> 00:17:45.355
They check every time they enter and exit.

00:17:45.939 --> 00:17:47.274
<i>Only the Emperor</i>

00:17:47.357 --> 00:17:50.819
<i>and his blood relatives can enter
the rear palace without being eunuchs.</i>

00:17:51.320 --> 00:17:53.739
<i>Does that mean Lord Jinshi is...</i>

00:17:53.822 --> 00:17:55.866
<i>No, that can’t be.</i>

00:17:56.450 --> 00:17:57.618
Speaking of eunuchs,

00:17:57.701 --> 00:18:00.537
have you heard about the new recruits?

00:18:02.122 --> 00:18:04.666
<i>Xiaolan and Shisui mentioned it.</i>

00:18:04.750 --> 00:18:08.712
I've heard rumors,
about 30 of them entered, right?

00:18:08.796 --> 00:18:10.422
Exactly!

00:18:10.506 --> 00:18:14.218
Many of them are young and good-looking,
so everyone's excited!

00:18:14.843 --> 00:18:17.137
The other day,
one of them got tangled up with

00:18:17.221 --> 00:18:20.682
a lower-ranked consort while preparing
the bath. It was quite the scene!

00:18:20.766 --> 00:18:23.185
<i>He actually went to check them out?</i>

00:18:24.019 --> 00:18:25.938
When exactly do you plan to tell her?

00:18:26.021 --> 00:18:27.898
Eventually.

00:18:27.981 --> 00:18:31.777
Your attitude is
so obvious, it's unnatural.

00:18:32.277 --> 00:18:35.781
Even Maomao looked at you
like you were a dried-up worm.

00:18:37.241 --> 00:18:39.159
Shut up. I know.

00:18:40.119 --> 00:18:43.831
If you don’t decide soon,
things will get messy.

00:18:43.914 --> 00:18:47.209
You want me to bring her over
to our side immediately, right?

00:18:47.292 --> 00:18:50.003
But the strategist will intervene.

00:18:50.087 --> 00:18:52.548
Fight poison with poison.

00:18:54.591 --> 00:18:56.635
<i>Dai Kan Lakan.</i>

00:18:56.718 --> 00:18:59.847
<i>A man who took his family’s estate from
his biological father and half-brother</i>

00:18:59.930 --> 00:19:01.723
<i>years ago,
becoming the head of the Luo clan.</i>

00:19:02.474 --> 00:19:04.977
<i>Even the emperor acknowledges him.</i>

00:19:05.936 --> 00:19:07.938
<i>Despite holding the rank
of Grand Commandant,</i>

00:19:08.021 --> 00:19:11.567
<i>he remains unaffiliated with any faction,
deftly avoiding entanglements.</i>

00:19:12.401 --> 00:19:14.778
<i>Many have tried to strike him down,</i>

00:19:14.862 --> 00:19:18.740
<i>but those who dared
suffered far worse than just burns.</i>

00:19:20.075 --> 00:19:22.077
<i>No one understands</i>

00:19:22.161 --> 00:19:23.996
<i>what goes on inside his head.</i>

00:19:24.538 --> 00:19:26.081
<i>The unspoken rule in court</i>

00:19:26.165 --> 00:19:29.084
<i>is to avoid him.</i>

00:19:29.751 --> 00:19:33.046
<i>But if I plan to bring Maomao in,</i>

00:19:33.130 --> 00:19:35.007
<i>I can’t ignore this.</i>

00:19:36.008 --> 00:19:38.010
<i>I want to tell her the truth.</i>

00:19:38.093 --> 00:19:40.012
<i>Why I hold this position,</i>

00:19:40.095 --> 00:19:42.598
<i>and why I hide my true identity.</i>

00:19:42.681 --> 00:19:44.099
<i>I want her to know.</i>

00:19:44.725 --> 00:19:47.269
<i>But after that, how will she react?</i>

00:19:51.315 --> 00:19:54.776
Another rear palace complaint?
Why so many?

00:19:55.527 --> 00:19:58.739
Half of them are concerning
Consort Loulan.

00:19:58.822 --> 00:20:00.449
They say that
she has too many palace women,

00:20:00.532 --> 00:20:03.869
her excessive use of elaborate outfits
is ruining the rear palace's aesthetics,

00:20:03.952 --> 00:20:05.370
and so on.

00:20:05.454 --> 00:20:07.331
Same complaints as always.

00:20:07.873 --> 00:20:10.959
This one is new, though.

00:20:13.629 --> 00:20:17.132
"Palace women are
flirting with the new eunuch."

00:20:17.966 --> 00:20:19.927
I could’ve guessed.

00:20:20.010 --> 00:20:23.263
Yes, we’ve assigned them
to physical labor for now.

00:20:23.847 --> 00:20:27.476
We’ll eventually transfer them to
suitable departments based on aptitude,

00:20:27.559 --> 00:20:30.520
but they were originally slaves
captured by foreign tribes.

00:20:31.021 --> 00:20:32.773
We need to be cautious.

00:20:34.316 --> 00:20:37.778
I suppose we should take a look
at least for formality’s sake.

00:20:37.861 --> 00:20:39.238
Yes.

00:20:39.321 --> 00:20:42.407
- What a hassle.
- Let's just do it.

00:20:44.534 --> 00:20:46.620
The ones with white sashes
are the new eunuchs.

00:20:47.496 --> 00:20:49.998
They’re thin and seem nervous.

00:20:50.999 --> 00:20:53.710
<i>Even after gaining freedom,</i>

00:20:53.794 --> 00:20:57.381
<i>former slaves struggle
to live like ordinary citizens.</i>

00:20:57.464 --> 00:21:01.051
<i>In some ways,
the rear palace is a suitable refuge.</i>

00:21:05.472 --> 00:21:06.932
<i>So that’s the infamous new eunuch, huh?</i>

00:21:07.557 --> 00:21:09.851
What happened to his left arm?

00:21:09.935 --> 00:21:11.895
He was severely beaten,

00:21:11.979 --> 00:21:14.898
leaving his left side partially numb.

00:21:15.399 --> 00:21:18.735
His body is covered in scars,
and he refuses to show his skin.

00:21:18.819 --> 00:21:19.736
I see.

00:21:21.613 --> 00:21:23.907
He’s quite popular, though.

00:21:23.991 --> 00:21:26.285
Yes, he’s smart

00:21:26.368 --> 00:21:28.578
and knows how to handle
the palace women well.

00:21:30.539 --> 00:21:33.792
- What?
- Like you can talk.

00:21:43.135 --> 00:21:46.388
- How are the new recruits?
- Lord Jinshi!

00:21:50.559 --> 00:21:52.269
They must still be adjusting, but in time,

00:21:52.352 --> 00:21:55.731
they’ll be assigned appropriate duties.
Be patient.

00:21:58.984 --> 00:22:02.279
What do we do?! That was ice

00:22:02.362 --> 00:22:04.406
meant for a high-ranking consort!

00:22:06.283 --> 00:22:09.494
Damn it! I’m done for!

00:22:12.873 --> 00:22:14.333
I’m so sorry...

00:23:46.007 --> 00:23:49.010
NEXT EPISODE PREVIEW

00:23:57.394 --> 00:23:59.437
{\an8}<i>The next episode is "Ice."</i>

00:23:59.521 --> 00:24:01.523
